    "Benny Suherman is a cofounder and the majority owner of Nusantara Sejahtera Raya, which runs Cinema XXI, Indonesia's largest cinema chain.",
    "Cinema XXI operates nearly 1,300 screens in 240 locations across the country.",
    "Suherman took the company public in August 2023 in a $150 million IPO.",
    "His sons Suryo and Arif are Nusantara Sejahtera Raya's president commissioner and director, respectively; son-in-law Hans Gunadi serves as its president director."
